  "title": "ハーレムの主の悩み",
  "created": 1775435186,
  "updated": 1775435473,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69d2fdaf71b29fc2e286b0ed",
      "text": "ハーレムの主の悩み",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775435186,
      "updated": 1775435186
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2fdb1000000000070e09a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775435186,
      "updated": 1775435186
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2fdc9000000000070e09d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775435209,
      "updated": 1775435300
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2fe24000000000070e0a0",
      "text": " この子と遊んでいるとき、あの子とは遊べない。どちらも大切な存在なのに",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775435300,
      "updated": 1775435473
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2fdf5000000000070e09f",
      "text": " 誰を愛でようか悩む",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775435253,
      "updated": 1775435350
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2fdb1000000000070e09b",
      "text": " メンバーが自分を取り合って喧嘩してしまう、喧嘩が起きないようにしたい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775435186,
      "updated": 1775435211
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2fe6f000000000070e0a2",
      "text": "  「[私のために争わないで]！」",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775435375,
      "updated": 1775435429
    },
    {
      "id": "69d2fe60000000000070e0a1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775435360,
      "updated": 1775435360
    }
  ]
}